    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, entirely free of scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather remains supple with no signs of wear, and all electronic components function perfectly. Mechanically, the car has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, and it drives as if it were brand new. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly preserved example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
