    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in impeccable condition, having been maintained to the highest standards of mechanical and aesthetic excellence. Every surface reflects a commitment to quality, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original showroom delivery. For the discerning collector who demands uncompromising integrity, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine specimen.",
